{"tid":773148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Impossible is nothing] 談糧庫“失火”：除非縱火，現代糧庫不可能著火","createTime":"2018-08-09T09:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T16:10:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae2b0f250d23c914afc16f3adac7fcb5200765e","tid":773148,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"大家可以先搜一搜，除了天朝，還有哪個國家的糧庫失火的？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.somii.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/liangku.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.somii.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Fliangku.jpg&h=71c85aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 現代糧庫不可能著火&mdash;-除非故意縱火。<br />\n<br />\n2. 現代糧庫的管理制度，特別是國家級別的糧庫，是從設計上保證了儲糧的安全。也不會存在以前的霉變，自損情況。而且這些損耗都是可計算，可測量的。<br />\n<br />\n3. 每個儲倉的溫度、濕度控制都是計算機監控的。每個中空底座都是可以放置熏蒸藥物，殺滅糧食蟲害，通過多孔鋼管一直深入到糧食堆裡面。所以，糧食自燃是不可能發生的事情。<br />\n<br />\n最後一點，糧庫的內部不是油庫，幾乎沒有可燃物質。即使是發生火災，噴淋頭也會在5秒之內完全撲滅內部火源，當然，如果是故意放火，那就另說了。<br />\n<br />\n據說是著火了，我就不知道是什麼東西在燒？糧庫的頂蓋根本是點不著的！<br />\n<br />\n居然有那麼多火點？這大風也太大了吧？能刮進全密封的倉室？說胡話也不能對著電視說啊？<br />\n<br />\n20年前糧庫的安全設計，（防老鼠，防盜，防水，防地震這裡就不說了）大家想想，20年前就用單片機全部做了安全防護，現在的技術還需要操這份心麼？<br />\n<br />\n國家級每個糧庫，投資都是過千萬的。不可能失火！<br />\n<br />\n所以，糧庫著火就是一個天大的笑話。<br />\n<br />\n至於糧庫裡面的貓膩，我也知道一些：<br />\n1. 是存糧置換，存在巨大的利益。新糧食和陳糧食的差價，簡直是嚇死人。<br />\n<br />\n2. 糧食等級差價，在裡面倒騰也是巨大的利益。<br />\n<br />\n3. 高額報損，虛報庫存數等等，都是撈錢的門路。<br />\n<br />\n4. 糧庫的領導，不敢說100%有問題，，，，嘿嘿，不說了。<br />\n<br />\n轉載請註明：搜秘 - 全球視野關注中國 &raquo; 笑談糧庫&ldquo;失火&rdquo;：除非縱火，現代糧庫不可能著火<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.somii.com/jiedu/lksh.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.somii.com%2Fjiedu%2Flksh.html&d=4HARd12Fs2HlhsTp1kULodZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=0bf7d09d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.somii.com/jiedu/lksh.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DkI_rC4X0AA8Pc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDkI_rC4X0AA8Pc6.jpg&h=7002155c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n湖南衡陽三塘糧倉又起火了​​​​​！聲明：我想說的是，因為糧食能造酒，而酒的主要成分是酒精，而酒精是易燃的😁😁看吧！結論出來了――這和政府調查餘糧沒有關係。 。 。 。 。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jiangshangdxh31/status/1026320532113747968\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjiangshangdxh31%2Fstatus%2F1026320532113747968&d=4HARd12Fs2HlhsTp1kULodZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=a0b42dfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjiangshangdxh31%2Fstatus%2F1026320532113747968&h=e2084fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jiangshangdxh31/status/1026320532113747968</a>"},{"pid":"52a004fe1df528dadbf13620bd02cb6e457e8f5d","tid":773148,"uid":56428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"爆了 大飢荒不遠"},{"pid":"202b39233c73dde5504d49e01cd73326ef138173","tid":773148,"uid":39855,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"呢招係建国後，已經用過幾次。"},{"pid":"2bfcafcc5c9172a20fe41dbb1b9f8cbb76fdb4b4","tid":773148,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"202b39233c73dde5504d49e01cd73326ef138173","tid":773148,"uid":39855,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"呢招係建国後，已經用過幾次。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93057f13d2f81f5743edc5023751019fad5e626c","tid":773148,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"202b39233c73dde5504d49e01cd73326ef138173","tid":773148,"uid":39855,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"呢招係建国後，已經用過幾次。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi